item.description: I’m here to share some interesting links. I do not have much time writing the blog now. Recently I have been working on CodeFalling/MacGesture on Github. If you are interested in it, go and have a look. Here are the links to share: https://twitter.com/PoolpOrg/status/694593152670437376 https://github.com/wellle/targets.vim http://thecodelesscode.com/case/225 https://twitter.com/zhangyuze320602/status/706457155763712000 I have done reading the biography of Steve Jobs. Great book.
